org.jboss.wise.core.client.consumer

Class WiseCXFConsumerImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jboss.ws.api.tools.WSContractConsumer
      • org.jboss.wise.core.client.consumer.WiseCXFConsumerImpl

  • public class WiseCXFConsumerImpl
extends org.jboss.ws.api.tools.WSContractConsumer
    A WSContractConsumer for CXF stack; this is basically a copy of the JBossWS-CXF 4.1.0 implementation, to early consume the fix for JBWS-3520 which is blocking for Wise 2.0 on AS 7 as it's the only workaround for WISE-179. This currently also include a workaround for CXF-4833.
    Author:
    alessio.soldano@jboss.com
